reviews.review_text: I always love a show from the 80's Even if it wasn't the best show, it was still a show! I love the 80's dead, my favorite years. Even though I wasn't even contemplated yet, I love the dead and always will. This show wasn't their greatest, but it's still better than Vince going of and wailing for no apparent reason. The Get Back maybe be pretty bad but they attempted it! Brent saves it, making it listenable. Jerry's on during Eyes as well, the mess up in the beginning just adds to the greatness of it! I'm just happy that it's available.
great show love the vibe and love bobby forgetting lyrics to jack straw, classic!
